# AXIOM Nabla node seed list — bootstrap host:port set for fresh
# wallet installs. Community-maintained: PR against axiom-dist to
# add / retire entries. The wallet's NablaPicker discovers more
# nodes via gossip after the seed set boots it up.
#
# Format (per sdk/core/src/app.rs::parse_nabla_nodes_list, 2026-05-14):
#   <name><TAB><host:tcp_port>
# - <name>: operator-chosen UTF-8 (genesis: Greek letters
#   alpha..kappa; non-genesis: penguin species, free-form).
# - HTTP port is auto-derived as tcp_port - 1074
#   (see sdk/src/nabla.rs::derive_http_addr).
alpha	172.20.0.42:7300
beta	172.20.0.42:7301
gamma	172.20.0.42:7302
delta	172.20.0.42:7303
epsilon	172.20.0.42:7304
zeta	172.20.0.42:7305
eta	172.20.0.42:7306
theta	172.20.0.42:7307
iota	172.20.0.42:7308
kappa	172.20.0.42:7309
